abstract: >
  A vendor-neutral synchronization layer for Asset Administration Shell (AAS) 
  digital twins using delta-CRDT anti-entropy replication. Addresses the gap 
  where AAS specifications explicitly leave synchronization and caching to 
  implementations, providing a reusable, standards-aligned solution for 
  multi-site deployments with offline-first capabilities.
